Revision history
################

0.1 Tue 12th July 2005

	- First public release


0.2 Wed 13th July 2005

	- Updated POD documentation


0.3 Wed 10th August 2005
	
	- Checking for spaces in build script
	- Changed makefile for build_script
	- You can now pass in a flag (install_module) to install the module.
	- Test output is now being supressed
	- You can now use build as well as make
	- Implemented nmake for windows
	- You can now have your tests run at random or in order
	- Skipping of tests implemented
	- Updated the POD documentation a bit more
